element.name: Dib Dib by moyle, Traditional Cache (1/1)
element.description:
I HAVE CHANGED THE CO-ORDINATES FOR THIS CACHE.
The old hiding place is no longer usable so I have moved the cache, it is still in the same general area.
A very easy cache. It was difficult to get accurate coordinates because of the trees but that should not put you off.
element.encoded-hints: NEW: at your feet near an entrance not watched by CCTV!!!
